      <Description>This data product contains monthly plots of iron ion charge state.  
Different panels give (1) color-coded counts of iron vs. charge state
and time, plus intensity-time profiles of (2) average charge state, 
(3) a measure of counting statistics and (4) solar wind flow speed.</Description>
